</ol>

<h3><strong><span>Lecture-hall</span></strong></h3>

<p>Major events of&nbsp;the &ldquo;Money of&nbsp;The Future&rdquo; will take place in&nbsp;Life.HALL, such as&nbsp;lectures, presentations and performances from the best fintech-experts, bankers, financial experts, entrepreneurs and officials. The full agenda is&nbsp;available at&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://prog.finovations.ru">prog.finovations.ru</a> </strong>and mobile application &ldquo;Life-Session&rdquo; in&nbsp;GooglePlay and AppStore.</p>

<h3><strong>Lounge-zone</strong></h3>

<p>At&nbsp;LifePay Market:Food&amp;Art lounge-zone the guests will get the pleasure of&nbsp;listening to&nbsp;the lectures on&nbsp;art, fashion, literature, gadgets and life-style. Here you can taste trendy street-food and beverages from Double B, Pueroport, Kotleta, Plov№&nbsp;1, TsaTsaFood. Here you can also purchase gadgets and accessories from Coob-Wood and Twinkle. Food&amp;Art is&nbsp;a&nbsp;cash-free zone where all the merchants will be&nbsp;supplied with LifePay+LifePAD to&nbsp;accept cards.</p>

